com.providenceuniversal.gim

Interface ClientMessage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Authentication, ChatHistoryRequest, ChatMessage, ContactsRequest, User, UserDisconnection

    public interface ClientMessage
extends Serializable
    The ClientMessage interface, is a marker interface representing a request from the client to the server. It is one of the super-ordinate types representing a message that can be sent between the client and server (the other being ServerMessage).

    1.0
